  "title": "Crimes and Offenses; the Attorney General concurrent jurisdiction with district attorneys to conduct criminal prosecutions of violent crimes, illegal immigration offenses, and fentanyl offenses; provide",
  "from_organization": "~{\"classification\": \"upper\"}",
